OpenVR version 0.01
========================

Perl bindings to the Valve OpenVR library

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   git clone https://github.com/Corion/Perl-OpenVR.git
   cd Perl-OpenVR
   cpanm --installdeps .
   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

https://github.com/ValveSoftware/openvr

